asset.hookText: Hi Tremain, we read your review on our site. It sounds like something isn't put together quite right on your SteamVac, otherwise it should dispense the liquid just fine.  We think it's an easy fix though. We put a video together to help get your shampooer working as it should. We hope this helps. Let us know if you need further assistance afterwards. Thanks so much! -Felicia
